 Fantasy. First, interstellar planning at our stage is wishing and nothing else. Second, burning fuel to push fuel to push fuel to push fuel to push fuel to push fuel to push fuel (love copy &amp; paste, and it's appropriate to describing the rocket equation) is silly for interstellar travel.<br>
