<br>
Another sad fact is that The USA and the Russians are at this very moment on the verge of destroying their stockpiles of weapons grade Plutonium. So where will the fuel for ORION come from if the piss ants are successful in getting Russia and the US to throw away the only source of energy that could open interplanetary Space to human exploration and Industrialization? <br>
<br>
To make these creeps happy I guess we should start thinking about a propulsion system that eats toxic waste and spits new age perfume out of its ass. <br>
